=='''TALALIT N UNAVAḌ AQVAYLI UƐḌIL'''==

'''TANAḌT N° GZM/2010/02/ASAN/05'''

Aselway n Unavaḍ aqvayli uɛḍil

- S usiked ɣer welɣu n Umussu adelsan amaziɣ - Agraw aɣelnaw n 5 yunyu 2001;

- S usiked ɣer tɣettisin n Weswir imseddes n umussu n Timanit i Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen (MAK) n 14/08/2007

d yiḍrisen-is imenzayen yellan d Asenfar n Timanit n Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen (PAK) d Urkawal n Yizerfan n Wegdud Aqvayli d Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen (CDK);

- S usiked ɣer usveddi n Unavaḍ Aqvayli Uɛḍil n 21/04/2010;

- S usiked ɣer tuzzeya n Useqqamu Aɣelnaw n Umussu n Timanit i Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen n 23/05/2010 yessersen M. Ferhat Mehenni, 

s uẓarisem-is Ferḥat At Sɛid, d aselway n Unavaḍ Aqvayli;

- S usiked ɣer tegrayin i n-rrant, deg 29/05/2010, tseqqamutt n uxemmem d tin n uciweṛ d usqerdec, yettwasvedden ass n 21/04/2010

IGZEM ITT

Amagrad I : Yettwasvedd-ed Unavaḍ Aqvayli Uɛḍil deg yinig, di Lpari.

Amagrad II : Win i t-yessulin d Aselway n Unavaḍ.

Amagrad III : Iswi-s d aslali n teɣsar tunṣivin n Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen d ugenses-nnsent ɣer udem n tejmaɛt tagraɣlant.

Amagrad IV : Ad idum alamma yeḍṛa-d usteɛṛef unṣiv yiss d usteɛṛef s Tmurt n Yiqvayliyen d agdud yakk d aɣlan sɣur n Uwanak azzayri.

Amagrad V : Amḍan n yiɛeggalen-is ur yerkid ara. Taluft-a terza tamuɣli n uselway-is ara yeṭṭfen ṛṛay s uciweṛ n tseqquma tinselkamin n Umussu n Tmanit n Tmurt n Yeqvayliyen (MAK).
Amagrad VI : Ɣef leḥsav n wakken yella umagrad V n tanaḍt-agi ya, yezmer uselway a d-yesseḍṛu ijeddilen iɣelfanen acemma icaweṛ tiseqquma tinselkamin n MAK.

Amagrad VII : Seg wass-a d tsawent, tanaḍt-a tegga leɛnaya.

Amagrad VIII : Tanaḍt-a a d-teffeɣ deg Weɣmis Unṣiv n Unavaḍ.

Imugg ass n 31 Mayu 2010

Aselway n Unavaḍ, Ferḥat At Sɛid

=='''Aɣmis Unṣiv n Unavaḍ aqvayli uɛḍil <ref>http://www.anavad.org/-le-journal-officiel-du,025-.html?lang=taq</ref>'''==

Iswi n weɣmis unṣiv n Unavaḍ Aqvayli Uɛḍil d asufeɣ s wevrid n tira n tgezmin tunṣivin yettaṭṭaf Unavaḍ.
Tigezmin-a rzant : 

-Aɛeggen n yineɣlafen d yemḍebbren imeqranen n unavaḍ (Imarayen imatuyen, imḍebbren n tedvelt n yeɣlifen, inemhalen iɣelfanen), ass m’ara d-vedden d wass m’ara ifak leqdic-nsen, 

-Asnulfu n tuddsiwin, 

-Isuḍaf n Unavaḍ.

Aɣmis unṣiv n Unavaḍ iteffeɣ-d s tutlayt taqvaylit d tutlayt tafṛansist.

== '''TAKARḌA N TNEKKIT TAQVAYLIT (KNQ)''' ==

[[Tugna:Cartedidenditkabyle.jpg|thumb| Takarḍa n Tnekkit Taqvaylit]]
Seld timlilit n Wegraw Amatu umussu n timanit di Fransa n wass 18/01/09, i deg d-yella umeslay ɣef wesnulfu n TKARḌA N TNEKKIT TAQVAYLIT. 

Seld asqerdec i d-iḍefren asarg n Mass Ferḥat At Sεid, Aqerru umussu, ass n 12/09/2009 di Tmeɣra n Talsa di Lpari ɣef yismawen n Yeqvayliyen di tmurt-nsen.

Imi nefren a nerr tajmilt i yimezwura nneɣ u a nefk azal i yesmawen i deg ṭṭfen d igiman n iseggasen s yiwen uzamul yecvan takarda n tnekkit.
